destinations.name: Kakamega Forest
destinations.description: Come explore indigenous trees with a tour guide, and get a chance at camping.

destinations.name: Watamu
destinations.description: Relax on the white sandy beaches of the Indian Ocean, in the North Coast.

destinations.name: Mt. Kenya
destinations.description: A challenging but rewarding hike up Africa’s second-highest peak.

destinations.name: Amboseli National Park
destinations.description: Enjoy views of Mt. Kilimanjaro and elephant herds.

destinations.name: Maasai Mara
destinations.description: Come enjoy the wildebeest migration, with a chance of having breakfast in the wild.

destinations.name: Diani Beach
destinations.description: Enjoy the crystal-clear waters, luxury resorts, and thrilling water sports.

destinations.name: Lake Naivasha
destinations.description: Boat rides, bird watching, and breathtaking views of the Great Rift Valley.

destinations.name: Samburu National Reserve
destinations.description: Wildlife safaris with a chance to see the ‘Samburu Special Five’.

destinations.name: Hell's Gate National Park
destinations.description: Perfect for hiking, biking, and rock climbing, with breathtaking landscapes.

destinations.name: Tsavo National Park
destinations.description: Explore the vast landscapes, see lions, and visit the famous Mzima Springs.
